# Modern OPSEC Guide: Privacy & Security for 2025

This is a dark-themed, user-friendly resource providing up-to-date information on VPN services, email providers, domain registrars, hosting options, and practical OPSEC tips as of 2025.  

The guide is designed to help anyone looking to improve their online privacy and security with reliable, well-researched recommendations. Whether youâ€™re new to OPSEC or have experience, this site offers clear details on service logging policies, subpoena compliance, and other key factors that affect your anonymity.  

It also includes actionable advice for everyday online activities, such as gaming, programming, and communication, while maintaining strong operational security.  

This project is intended for educational purposes and to support privacy-conscious users in navigating the complex landscape of digital security.
